Breadcrumbs SUBHEADER AREA end planning a special occasion or business event? Let the Rooney’s Family make your event a special one. We have two party/meeting rooms available for your special occasion or business events! Our back dining area can accommodate from 15 to 100 people and our “pool room” can accommodate from 5 to 45 people. Ask about our food & drink options for your event such as having a limited options menu or, a buffet style dining experience. Call us at (321)724-8520 for more information & make your reservations today.
